al/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nOne piece此情不再<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我識識既烏索普，簡單d黎講就係一條廢柴，為左生存、活命，就算無恥都好，佢都照做。但當一d信念同伙伴被侵犯，佢就會行出黎，以巧破力，以機智、陰險、邪道、創意去戰勝強敵，佢係唯一一個角色係你唔會知佢點贏。雖然係仆街，但就好有型，仆住街咁贏。而狙擊王就係一個藉口去比另一個人格自己，去擁有力量。<br />\n<br />\n而唔撚係而加新世界，明明有能力係勁，話自己練左兩年，但比之前既心態重廢，唔再識以巧破力，狙擊王唔再出現，新世界之後我只睇到佢既懦弱，再冇懦弱裹面所衍生既強大，一味既廢柴刻劃，冇成長之餘，重要keep唔到以前既自己，令我真係信左佢既本質就係垃圾。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3d6ab27abe1816294c7d4f2f06dbd1b86c5a1f3","tid":244690,"uid":5303,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T21:43:03.000Z","msg":"Zoro,Robin"},{"pid":"e23d4dd77ad75a70ba76e39a276cd974df4c22c1","tid":244690,"uid":45591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T21:55:28.000Z","msg":"羅賓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"575f405ea0e77831608966527f5646f87c11694c","tid":244690,"uid":5831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T02:02:42.000Z","msg":"竟然冇人講tony?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> zero sanji都鐘意但最愛一定tony tony chopper<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又可愛又得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個故事又最正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我又個期開始睇one piece"},{"pid":"ca7161f278315627b6f9a7146e149e1b63fcfa77","tid":244690,"uid":115235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T02:06:53.000Z","msg":"Zoro <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d222a9bc4dadb90841dca163c001e3ba2d3b87f4","tid":244690,"uid":935